Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜先生冷靜下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣鬧下去  就由我來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在菈菈面前展現我男子漢氣概的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}雷恩  不要太勉強自己哦  會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我來解決你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺  旋輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沒事吧  雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了  梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}胸…胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放開美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要舔尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜先生  住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}西瓜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…夢夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用恐懼來讓它理解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  放開菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  快放開菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險  快躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做砍西瓜的遊戲  只要這樣做就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑感覺氣息來砍這一點  好像有點不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這西瓜還真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這樣西瓜先生也就死而無憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  害大家虛驚一場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都要來嘗一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  猿山人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  考得怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  98分  那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得那麼大聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜一直都考得好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時不多玩點可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說這分數也太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  結城君原來這麼笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭腦子笨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊  明天還要再考一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦啊  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之再不複習的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能振作起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛偷笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你學習還是努力下比較好  比如請教別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球上靠的就是學力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你周圍就有能幫你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼  都一燒解決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…有這麼聰明？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼久你都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人可擁有著在銀河也都家喻戶曉的天才頭腦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至曾經有居心叵測之徒想利用菈菈大人的頭腦開發武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在很早前問菈菈成績時…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是菈菈大人還沒記住地球文字的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是讀不懂題目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這才能只用在製造一些惡作劇道具上  可說是玉瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  洗完好舒服哦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別圍著毛巾就跑出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  又沒光著身子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼  是在學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都是一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道題目是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能教我倒是非常感謝  這身打扮稍微換下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  佩凱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道題目  只要代入這個公式就能解決哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  那這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是指數方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  菈菈真的是很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺  被梨斗表揚真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我來撿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好  心裡有雜念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不集中精神學習的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩凱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  電量耗盡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之先…遮…起…來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送杯咖啡來…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…習…學習…  學習…學…學習…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續加油吧  雖然不知道是在學什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}補考
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  本來記得的東西都全部忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別冷不防就抱過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣毫無進展啊  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得菈菈應該多瞭解些戀愛知識才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛知識？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼樣吸引梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今天專門給菈菈樣好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  現在流行的「如何戀愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\an8\fad(200,0)}攻陷男人之一百計
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個做參考將結城攻陷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將梨斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛嗎  雖然看上去很困難  但只有努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先邀請他去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能直截了當地說約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在說話時自然而然提出才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡逛逛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天一定要努力吸引住梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法少女恭子  不管什麼  都一燒解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法少女恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  既然有事情就趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會時說話要害羞  讓他對你的好感提高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞…  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  今天  在學校過得也好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是我說話的方式不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的法寶在於  進退有方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}「進退有方」字面上的意思是「推」和「拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然惹他生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要這樣胡鬧就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊  必須想點辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為對方喜歡類型的女孩也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如「奇幻型」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「我是某某星人」之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨…  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我  是戴比魯克星人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？奇幻型好像不是梨斗的喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  其它還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}傲嬌型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說菈菈  感覺你今天怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自作多情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不喜歡梨斗  一點感覺都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  菈菈  這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的話只是掩飾  真正喜歡是用行動來表示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就秒殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再搭配暴露和大膽的衣服誘惑他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧一切將他撲倒  征服他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始吧  佩凱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大膽的服裝是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然有些不太明白  總之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這身打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了那些話  但我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈…菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後下一步該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  究竟怎麼啦  今天的菈菈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被她牽著鼻子走  真有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然按書上努力去做了  到最後還是失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼眼淚會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說菈菈是因為這才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾像這樣兩人繞路逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別黏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  梨斗  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  明天去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當然是去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙姬小姐  請說幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙姬小姐  已經到時間了
